# ============================================================
# Navin Frontend — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your actual values.
# Vite only exposes env vars prefixed with VITE_ to the client.
# ============================================================

# Required: Backend API base URL
# The Axios client in src/services/api/client.ts uses this to
# route all API requests. If missing, the app throws a runtime error.
# Example for local development with the navin-backend repo:
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api